<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَإِلَّا: فَمِنْهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- ثُمَّ يَطُوفُ، وَيَسْعَى، وَيُقَصِّرُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> أَرْكَانُ الحَجِّ أَرْبَعَةٌ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> إِحْرَامٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَوُقُوفٌ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَطَوَافٌ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> وَسَعْيٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَوَاجِبَاتُه سَبْعَةٌ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> إِحْرَامُ مَارٍّ عَلَى <span class="c2">(١)</span> مِيقَاتٍ مِنْهُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَوُقُوفٌ إِلَى اللَّيْلِ إِنْ وَقَفَ نَهَاراً.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَمَبِيتٌ بِمُزْدَلِفَةَ إِلَى بَعْدِ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> نِصْفِهِ إِنْ وَافَاهَا قَبْلَهُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> وَبِمِنًى لَيَالِيَهَا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[٥]</span> وَالرَّمْيُ مُرَتَّباً.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في (أ) و (ج): عن. والمثبت موافق لكافي المبتدي.<br>(٢) قوله: (بعد) سقطت من (د).</p> </div>